<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Netmarble [41 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/netmarble">Netmarble</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Netmarble Nexus [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/netmarble/netmarble-nexus">Netmarble Nexus</a> have officially <a href="https://twitter.com/ShanFro_nana/status/1941874783425048951" target="_blank">announced</a> <em><a title="Games > Shangri-La Frontier: The Seven Colossi" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/shangri-la-frontier-the-seven-colossi">Shangri-La Frontier: The Seven Colossi</a></em> for iOS and Android, two years after the game’s <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2023/07/netmarble-announces-shangri-la-frontier-game">initial teaser trailer</a>. <span id="more-977846"></span></p><p>The game will allow players to experience the world of <em>Shangri-La</em> in full 3D. Players can use one hand to battle giant bosses while alternating between two characters.</p><p>Watch the announcement trailer below.</p><h2><span>Announce Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="『シャングリラ・フロンティア ～七つの最強種～』アナウンストレーラー" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9-_RF3jbOq4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
